modules.description: This module creates an Async-based session manager using a provided backend. It handles session creation, retrieval, and expiration through functions like `generate`, `of_key`, and `clear`, and integrates with HTTP cookies via `of_header` and `to_cookie_hdrs`. It works with string-based keys and values, expiration periods in seconds, and Cohttp headers for session management in web applications.

This module creates an Async-based session manager using a provided backend. It handles session creation, retrieval, and expiration with functions like `generate`, `of_key`, and `clear`, while supporting HTTP cookie integration through `of_header` and `to_cookie_hdrs`. It works with string keys, expiration times in seconds, and Cohttp headers for managing sessions in web applications.
